Titolo: Bowser's Fury

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Bowser's Fury is a 2021 platform game bundled in with the Nintendo Switch release of Super Mario 3D World. The player controls Mario through Lake Lapcat, a 3D, cat-themed open world to complete challenges and collect "Cat Shines" to dispel a black sludge that's infecting the land and free Bowser (known as Fury Bowser) from its control. At irregular intervals, Bowser turns the world into apocalyptic night to rain fire on Mario and alter the environment. Its gameplay is based on 3D World.
The bundled release was reported to be the best-selling video game of February 2021 in the United States.

Genere: Platform 

Valutazione: N/A
